audioanalyze.quickdescript: transcribe audio/video/links to text using openai whisper model

convert.quickdescript: converts a file to different format based on uploaded file type or specified in the command.

downloader.quickdescript: download video/audio from social/music platforms (YouTube, Twitter, Instagram, SoundCLoud, Spotify) *Spotify may not result with a correct song if its not found on youtube.*

ifruitcall.quickdescript: Overlays your or specified user\'s pfp and username/nickname onto the GTA iFruit call screen

lyricfinder.quickdescript: Fings lyrics for a song from music platforms (YouTube, Spotify, SoundCloud)

riodejaneiro.quickdescript: Adds a Rio De Janeiro instagram filter over image/video

translate.quickdescript: translates text from autodetected language to English, or from one specified language to another.
